complement

public CMLBondSet complement(CMLBondSet bondSet2)
Returns complement of this bondSet with another. Creates new bondSet containing the bonds that are in this bondSet, and not the one supplied.

eg. as1 = {a1, a2, a3}; as2 = {a2, a4}
(as1) complement (as2) = {a1, a3}
(as2) complement (as1) = {a4}

Parameters:
bondSet2 - bondSet to complement; if null assumed empty
Returns:
bondSet

union

public CMLBondSet union(CMLBondSet bondSet2)
                 throws CMLRuntimeException
Returns union of this bondSet with another. Creates new bondSet containing the bonds that are in this bondSet, and/or the one supplied. (Inclusive or)

eg. as1 = {a1, a2, a3}; as2 = {a2, a4}
(as1) union (as2) = (as2) union (as1) = {a1, a2, a3, a4}

Parameters:
bondSet2 - bondSet to unite with
Returns:
bond set
Throws:
CMLRuntimeException

symmetricDifference

public CMLBondSet symmetricDifference(CMLBondSet bondSet2)
                               throws CMLException
Returns symmetric difference of this bondSet with another. Creates new bondSet containing the bonds that are in either bondSet, or the one supplied, but not both. (Exclusive or)

eg. as1 = {a1, a2, a3}; as2 = {a2, a4}
(as1) symmetric difference (as2) = {a1, a3, a4}

Parameters:
bondSet2 - bondSet to xor with
Returns:
bondSet
Throws:
CMLException
